## Locked Decisions

| # | Decision | Choice |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | Admin bootstrapping | Manual `role='admin'` in Supabase Dashboard |
| 2 | Gallery visibility | Public browsing (no auth). Auth for Favourite/Upload only |
