## Core Userflows

### 1. Admin content population
Admin → `/admin/items/new` → upload image → fill metadata (title, prompt, AI model, settings) → assign tags/categories → Publish → item appears on `/gallery`.

### 2. Public discovery
Anonymous → `/gallery` → filter by category/tag → search → click card → `/gallery/[id]` → premium inspector (prompt, settings, attribution).

### 3. Favourite
Heart on card → if logged-out, redirect to `/login` → return → toggle favourite → visible in `/profile/favourites`.

### 4. User submission + moderation
User → `/profile/uploads/new` → item created as `state=pending_review`, `visibility=private`, image in private bucket → admin sees in `/admin/moderation` → Approve (copy image to public bucket, set `state=published`, `visibility=public`) OR Reject (add notes) → user sees status + notes in `/profile/uploads`.

