## Database Schema

### State Machine (single `state` field)

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> draft : Admin creates
    [*] --> pending_review : User submits
    draft --> published : Admin publishes
    pending_review --> published : Admin approves
    pending_review --> rejected : Admin rejects
    rejected --> pending_review : User resubmits
    published --> archived : Admin archives
    archived --> published : Admin restores
```

