## Storage

| Bucket | Read | Write | Delete | Purpose |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| `inspiration-public` | Anyone | Admins only | Admins only | Published gallery images |
| `inspiration-private` | Owner + Admin | Auth users (own folder) | Owner + Admin | Pending review uploads |

- **Path convention**: `{auth.uid()}/{uuid}.{ext}`
- **Accepted types**: `image/jpeg`, `image/png`, `image/webp`, `image/gif`
- **Max file size**: 10 MB
- **On approval**: Admin copies file from `inspiration-private` → `inspiration-public`, updates `image_url`

**Storage RLS scoping** (enforced in Supabase Storage policies):
```sql
-- inspiration-private: users can only interact with their own folder
-- INSERT
bucket_id = 'inspiration-private'
  AND (storage.foldername(name))[1] = auth.uid()::text
-- SELECT
bucket_id = 'inspiration-private'
  AND ((storage.foldername(name))[1] = auth.uid()::text OR is_admin())
-- DELETE
bucket_id = 'inspiration-private'
  AND ((storage.foldername(name))[1] = auth.uid()::text OR is_admin())

-- inspiration-public: admin-only write/delete, public read
-- SELECT: true (public)
-- INSERT/DELETE: is_admin()
```

