## Security

| Concern | Mitigation |
|---|---|
| Privilege escalation | `is_admin()` in RLS + middleware + Server Actions |
| User uploads | Scoped to `profile_id/` folder; type + size validated server-side |
| Service role key | Server Actions only; never in client bundle |
| Delete published items | Users submit `delete_requests`; only admins can physically delete |
| Audit trail | All admin mutations logged to `admin_action_log` |
| XSS | React auto-escaping; no `dangerouslySetInnerHTML` |
| CSRF | Next.js Server Actions use POST + origin check |

## Accessibility

- `:focus-visible` rings on all interactive elements
- ARIA labels on icon-only buttons
- Heading hierarchy (`h1` → `h2` → `h3`)
- Colour contrast ≥ 4.5:1 (WCAG AA)
- `prefers-reduced-motion` wraps animations
- Focus trap in modals/dialogs
- Keyboard-navigable gallery grid
- Alt text on all images
- Skip-to-content link
- `aria-live` for form errors and toasts

